rows.label: tlk41100121_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You know how monsters drop gold
when you beat them?

rows.label: tlk41100121_01_msg0003
rows.name:
That's 'cos they really, really like
collecting shiny things! Bet you
didn't know that!

rows.label: tlk41100121_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Eh, knowing random stuff like that
isn't going to help me get better
at swimming.

rows.label: tlk41100121_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I keep trying and trying, but I'm still
rubbish at it. Funny, huh?
A Gulan kid who can't swim...
